## Movement
Move left|h / Left
Move down|j / Down
Move up|k / Up
Move right|l / Right
Move next word start|w
Move previous word start|b
Move next WORD start|W
Move previous WORD start|B
Move next WORD end|E
Find 'till next char|t
Find next char|f
Find 'till previous char|T
Find previous char|F
Go to line number <n>|G
Repeat last motion (f, t or m)|Alt-.
Move to start of line|Home
Move to end of line|End
Move page up|Ctrl-b / PageUp
Move page down|Ctrl-f / PageDown
Move half page up|Ctrl-u
Move half page down|Ctrl-d
Jump forward on jumplist|Ctrl-i
Jump backward on jumplist|Ctrl-o
Save current selection to jumplist|Ctrl-s
